<description>&lt;div class=&#34;alert alert-info small bg-info&#34; role=&#34;alert&#34;&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;text-muted&#34;&gt;code for article&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/pfeilbr/aws-codebuild-local-playground&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fab fa-github fa-sm&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&amp;nbsp;pfeilbr/aws-codebuild-local-playground&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;resources&#34;&gt;Resources&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/devops/announcing-local-build-support-for-aws-codebuild/&#34;&gt;Announcing Local Build Support for AWS CodeBuild&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;running&#34;&gt;Running&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# build CodeBuild image locally &lt;/span&gt;
git clone https://github.com/aws/aws-codebuild-docker-images.git
&lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; aws-codebuild-docker-images/ubuntu/standard/2.0
docker build -t aws/codebuild/standard:2.0 .

&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# pull  CodeBuild local agent&lt;/span&gt;
docker pull amazon/aws-codebuild-local:latest --disable-content-trust&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# cd to directory containing `buildspec.yml`&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# NOTE: script was previously downloaded to `~/bin/codebuild_build.sh`&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; basic-01
codebuild_build.sh -i &lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;aws/codebuild/standard:2.0&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; -a &lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;artifact-output&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; -c

&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
